<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer2891857157799001862">Ted Byfield is a New York–based independent researcher and writer. He served for over a decade on the design faculty of the New School University, and is a former visiting fellow at Yale Law School’s Information Society Project. He co-founded the Open Syllabus Project research network, and since 1998 has co-moderated the  mailing list.</span>

</div>
